Mia McKenna-Bruce https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mia_McKenna-Bruce 0 Mia Sasha McKenna-Bruce (born 3 July 1997) is an English actress, best known for her roles as Tee Taylor in Tracy Beaker Returns and in spin-off series The Dumping Ground; as Penny Branning in EastEnders; and as Ashley Tyler in 2009 film The Fourth Kind.
